full_text:
Just discovered that iOS will crazily vary font size of web pages unless you chant the magic spell `-webkit-text-size-adjust: none;`

What the fuck is happening in this image, this font is all set to a single size.

Second image is after the CSS fix. https://t.co/lqi8h6LcRI
